'''Ramón Pons''' (13 October 1940 – 21 April 2014) was a [[Spanish people|Spanish]] film, stage and television actor. He appeared in more than 15 films from 1970 on.<ref>{{cite news|title=Ramón Pons, el galán de los sesenta|url=http://www.madridiario.es/cultura/necrologica/ramon-pons/410870|accessdate=24 April 2014|newspaper=Madridiario|date=22 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Fallece en Madrid el actor valenciano Ramón Pons|url=http://www.lavanguardia.com/local/valencia/20140422/54405204438/fallece-en-madrid-el-actor-valenciano-ramon-pons.html|accessdate=24 April 2014|newspaper=La Vanguardia|date=22 April 2014}}</ref>

